---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Services">
<main id="main">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="svc-hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="eyebrow">Services</div>
        <h1 class="display" data-reveal>What we can help you <em class="italic-accent">build</em>.</h1>
        <p class="section-lede" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="100">Five disciplines we focus on. Every project gets the same process: slow at the start,
          quick at the end.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SERVICE CARDS -->
    <section class="section-tight">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="svc-cards">

          <!-- 01 UX -->
          <article class="svc-card" id="ux" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="0">
            <div class="num">01</div>
            <div class="core">
              <h3>UX Design</h3>
              <p>Research, wireframing, user flow, and prototyping. For products still chasing product-market fit, or
                ones that exist but need a full redesign because the UX no longer matches its users.</p>
              <span class="price-tag">Starting at · IDR 8M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="deliverables">
              <h4>Includes</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>User research &amp; interviews</li>
                <li>Information architecture</li>
                <li>Wireframes (lo-fi → mid-fi)</li>
                <li>User flow &amp; journey map</li>
                <li>Interactive prototype</li>
                <li>Usability testing notes</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-col">
              <a href="about.html#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Discuss <span class="arr">→</span></a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- 02 UI -->
          <article class="svc-card" id="ui" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="100">
            <div class="num">02</div>
            <div class="core">
              <h3>UI Design</h3>
              <p>Visual design, design system, and component library. For products with a clear concept that need a
                consistent look, real character, and something easy for the dev team to maintain.</p>
              <span class="price-tag">Starting at · IDR 6M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="deliverables">
              <h4>Includes</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Visual design (light + dark)</li>
                <li>Design tokens (color, type, spacing)</li>
                <li>Figma component library</li>
                <li>Responsive layouts</li>
                <li>Design system documentation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-col">
              <a href="about.html#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Discuss <span class="arr">→</span></a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- 03 Web -->
          <article class="svc-card" id="web" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="200">
            <div class="num">03</div>
            <div class="core">
              <h3>Website Development</h3>
              <p>End-to-end website development. Good for company profiles, light dashboards, or web apps that need real
                interactivity. We use a modern stack that&rsquo;s easy to maintain.</p>
              <span class="price-tag">Starting at · IDR 15M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="deliverables">
              <h4>Includes</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Frontend development</li>
                <li>CMS integration (if needed)</li>
                <li>Responsive across devices</li>
                <li>Basic SEO setup</li>
                <li>Performance optimization</li>
                <li>Deployment &amp; domain setup</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-col">
              <a href="about.html#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Discuss <span class="arr">→</span></a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- 04 Landing -->
          <article class="svc-card" id="landing" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="300">
            <div class="num">04</div>
            <div class="core">
              <h3>Landing Page Development</h3>
              <p>A single-page landing that converts — from design to live in 1–2 weeks. For campaigns, product
                launches, or new brands that need to be online fast.</p>
              <span class="price-tag">Starting at · IDR 5M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="deliverables">
              <h4>Includes</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Wireframe + copywriting support</li>
                <li>UI design (mobile + desktop)</li>
                <li>Development &amp; deploy</li>
                <li>Form integration</li>
                <li>Analytics setup (GA4 / Plausible)</li>
                <li>Domain &amp; hosting setup</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-col">
              <a href="about.html#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Discuss <span class="arr">→</span></a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- 05 Brand -->
          <article class="svc-card" id="brand" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="400">
            <div class="num">05</div>
            <div class="core">
              <h3>Brand &amp; Logo Guideline</h3>
              <p>Logo, brand book, and a visual system that&rsquo;s ready to hand off to any team or vendor. Not just a
                pretty logo — a system that keeps your brand consistent wherever it&rsquo;s used.</p>
              <span class="price-tag">Starting at · IDR 4M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="deliverables">
              <h4>Includes</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Logo design (3 alternatives)</li>
                <li>Color &amp; typography system</li>
                <li>Logo usage rules</li>
                <li>Pattern / illustration system</li>
                <li>Brand book PDF</li>
                <li>Working files (Figma)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-col">
              <a href="about.html#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Discuss <span class="arr">→</span></a>
            </div>
          </article>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROCESS -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <div class="eyebrow">How We Work</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Slow at the start, <em class="italic-accent">quick</em> at the end.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="process-band pattern-wrap">
          <div class="pat-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="process-step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="0">
              <div class="num">01</div>
              <h4>Briefing</h4>
              <div class="dur">1–2 days</div>
              <p>Discovery call, scope alignment. We make sure we understand the problem first.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="80">
              <div class="num">02</div>
              <h4>Exploration</h4>
              <div class="dur">3–5 days</div>
              <p>Mood board, wireframes, direction. Two or three directions to test before committing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="160">
              <div class="num">03</div>
              <h4>Design</h4>
              <div class="dur">1–3 weeks</div>
              <p>Visual design, prototype, interaction details. Reviews every week.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="240">
              <div class="num">04</div>
              <h4>Iteration</h4>
              <div class="dur">1 week</div>
              <p>One big revision round, not small ping-pong loops that wear everyone out.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="320">
              <div class="num">05</div>
              <h4>Handoff</h4>
              <div class="dur">1–2 days</div>
              <p>File delivery, documentation, and 2 weeks of handoff support.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="section" id="faq">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <div class="eyebrow">FAQ</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Common questions.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="100">
          <div class="accordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button class="accordion-trigger">How long does a project usually take? <span
                  class="icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="accordion-content">
                <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                  Depends on scope. Landing page: 1–2 weeks. Company profile website: 3–5 weeks. Larger UX/UI work
                  (dashboards, SaaS): 4–8 weeks. Branding: 3–4 weeks. We give a firm estimate after reviewing your
                  brief.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button class="accordion-trigger">How many revisions can I request? <span class="icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="accordion-content">
                <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                  Usually 2 big revision rounds — enough for projects with a solid brief. Extra revisions are billed
                  hourly at a transparent rate stated in the proposal.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button class="accordion-trigger">Is there a deposit? Can I pay in installments? <span
                  class="icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="accordion-content">
                <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                  50% deposit upfront before the project starts. The remaining 50% is due before final file handoff. For
                  projects above IDR 30M we can split into 3 installments (30/40/30).
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button class="accordion-trigger">Do you offer retainers or monthly arrangements? <span
                  class="icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="accordion-content">
                <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                  Yes. We have retainer packages starting from IDR 20M/month for teams that need ongoing design support.
                  A good fit for startups shipping every week.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button class="accordion-trigger">What if the service I need isn&rsquo;t on the list? <span
                  class="icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="accordion-content">
                <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                  Just ask. If we can do it well, we&rsquo;ll say so. If we can&rsquo;t, we&rsquo;ll recommend a studio
                  that&rsquo;s a better fit.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button class="accordion-trigger">Do you work with international clients? <span
                  class="icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="accordion-content">
                <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                  Yes, we&rsquo;ve worked with clients in Singapore and Australia. Communication in English, billing in
                  USD. Our time zone is WIB (UTC+7).
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <button class="accordion-trigger">How does communication work during a project? <span
                  class="icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="accordion-content">
                <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                  Primary channels: Slack or WhatsApp Business for daily updates, Notion for docs, Figma for design
                  reviews. Loom for longer walkthroughs. Async-first — meetings only when really necessary.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section-tight">
      <div class="cta-wrap">
        <div class="svc-cta" data-reveal>
          <h3>Got a project? <em>Let&rsquo;s discuss</em> it with us.</h3>
          <div class="btn-row">
            <a href="mailto:hello@rohaworks.com" class="btn btn-primary">Email Us <span class="arr">→</span></a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/[NO_WA]?text=Hi%20Roha" class="btn btn-outline-cream" target="_blank"
              rel="noopener">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>
